1653:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         initialization, calendar update or after wakeup from low power modes
1654:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         the software must first clear the RSF flag.
